Package: linktaxa
Type: Package
Title: Link two taxonomic reference lists
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2013-12-06
Author: Roland Kaiser
Maintainer: Roland Kaiser <kardinal.eros@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.1), stringdist
Suggests: pbapply
Description: Takes two character vectors of scientific taxon names and performs and exhaustive search for possible analogs. The package provides tools to accommodate linking against infra specific taxon.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Collate: isWhat.R
         stripWhat.R
         dropInfraspecific.R
         expandSensuStricto.R
         asSensuStricto.R
         addSensuStricto.R
         subHybrid.R
         seekTaxon.R
         judgePenalty.R
         zeroPenalty.R
         relaxPenalty.R
         compareGenus.R
         queuePenalty.R
         linktaxa.R

